post_title: FS: Over 50 Raw Commons - ALL SOLD
post_content:
Time to get of some commons. I got these in a lot and condition of them is surprisingly good. Some have light wrinkles and a few with a crease. Some appear to be trimmed, please look at the pics to determine your thoughts, I tried to call out ones that I think were. Several of these I’m considering subbing to SGC as I think they could get reasonable grades.

I’m available via PM, but please note that anyone saying SOLD on the post gets priority over ongoing negotiations.

Please add $3 for tracked shipping, regardless of how many bought.

Thanks for looking!
Jeff
